{
  "stem": "24163.4",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And there was a flag of Argentina hanging outside.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this was a major Nazi in town, but they had this flag hanging out there.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So I knew that that was all phony baloney.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And I went to open the gates, went into the house, and this was a beautiful home, a piano in the living room, one of these circular stairwells leading to the second floor.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And as I entered the house-- or just prior to that, I had heard from home that my grandmother had been deported and most likely was among those people who had not survived the camps.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I heard that when I was a soldier in Germany.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She had been deported in 1942.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was deported to-- she had moved to Holland and was deported from Holland either in '42 or '43-- I'm not sure when-- to a camp.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I had gotten a letter from home saying that she more than likely, because of her age-- already she was 84-- had not survived.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I entered this home, and there came an elegant German woman about my grandmother's age.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She came down this winding stairwell, and she looked dressed in black, very dignified, like my grandmother used to dress.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I see this woman come down.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And she says in a very arrogant German, [GERMAN]?",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I told her-- What you want?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "What do want?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "What you want?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told her that they have until 5 o'clock that evening to vacate the house, and not to take anything but blankets so they can sleep somewhere-- and I didn't care where-- and leave everything absolutely intact, and vacate the house.",
      "word_count": 42
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, she was so indignant.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I told her, I said, in German, I said that my grandmother looked very much like you.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
